{"tid":1774963,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術] 大家係用詞方面要有所改變！","createTime":"2019-12-08T14:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T10:02:07.000Z","uid":303462,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"60b457b0f9a161257d640f29bc9979469e1ee6e8","tid":1774963,"uid":303462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:19:09.000Z","msg":"點樣定義一個群體，同一件事，係好影響到大眾嘅觀感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如港共曱甴隊就好撚鍾意騎劫「暴力」呢個term，完全無視曱甴隊泯滅人性嘅所作所為，令大眾先入為主，見到「與暴力割席」就會下意識認為係手足嘅暴力，英文報紙入面嘅 escalated violence亦然 比警謊會水鳩曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我地要先發製人，重新定義曬所有 term<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我呢度拋磚引玉比幾個例子，當中好多手足都已經用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">愛國遊行 nationalist rally </span></strong><br />\n&rarr; 比人有正面影響，下意識無視過班只係一班收錢嘅 no stake<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>反民主遊行 anti-democratic rally<br />\n </strong>&rarr; 即時建立阻礙人類文明發展負面影響，而呢點亦都係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">建制派  pro-establishment camp</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>賣港派 (pro-Beijing camp? 有冇其他建議？）</strong><br />\n呢點已經有手足講左<br />\n呢班撚樣建設過乜柒先，賣港求榮就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後最重要嘅一點</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">香港政府</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>港共政府</strong><br />\n呢個政府從來都唔係服務緊香港人，佢冇資格成撚日騎劫代表我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9802ea5f07e6fc037255d1cbd7890f99c1a35886","tid":1774963,"uid":111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:20:45.000Z","msg":"語言影響思考"},{"pid":"87cf1fda3d474f6660630053a42f59f05bd047fb","tid":1774963,"uid":303462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9802ea5f07e6fc037255d1cbd7890f99c1a35886","tid":1774963,"uid":111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:20:45.000Z","msg":"語言影響思考"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:21:54.000Z","msg":"exactly<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be47a461e1c5722384b391f298c3b6e9003c0f56","tid":1774963,"uid":140218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:22:30.000Z","msg":"少數派 / 反民主派 / 親中派<br />\n有巴打咁樣提議過"},{"pid":"4d8d0f73d0f125b7a48a59fe9e27d9386f0dba1a","tid":1774963,"uid":303462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be47a461e1c5722384b391f298c3b6e9003c0f56","tid":1774963,"uid":140218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:22:30.000Z","msg":"少數派 / 反民主派 / 親中派<br />\n有巴打咁樣提議過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:28:29.000Z","msg":"最後建議左賣港派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有咩建議？term上嘅改變？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be95c2c4205f5a7e0b32781794aac713993ca55","tid":1774963,"uid":320078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:48:00.000Z","msg":"藍絲=反民主人士"},{"pid":"6e5a991670ca15c4f0791b29bdaeaa3102b09fef","tid":1774963,"uid":303462,"like":0,"d